definition: tree/wood/coffin/wooden/simple/numb/one of the eight categories of ancient musical instruments 八音[ba1 yin1]

sentences.english: The tent-shaped huts are made out of logs hammered together, which rest on floating barrels.
sentences.chinese: 那些帐篷状的棚屋由原木捶钉而成并依靠浮筒漂浮。

sentences.english: Cedar columns flare at their base as they prop up the Douglas fir logs overhead.
sentences.chinese: 雪松柱熠熠生辉地在支撑着上方的花旗松原木。

sentences.english: Log and wood pulp are large-volume imported forest products for China.
sentences.chinese: 原木和木浆是我国进口林产品中的大宗商品。

sentences.english: Right, only log and diamond trucks.
sentences.chinese: 猜对了，原木和钻石开采车。

sentences.english: Log products are the main products of forest enterprises.
sentences.chinese: 原木产品是森工企业主产品。

sentences.english: Our company is specialized in making wood-door . the product is natural , pure handmade and European style.
sentences.chinese: 我司的原木门产品突出原生态，纯手工，欧洲风格。

sentences.english: The logs were drifted down the stream to the saw-mills.
sentences.chinese: 原木顺流而下漂向锯木厂。

sentences.english: A log fire crackled in the fireplace.
sentences.chinese: 一节原木在壁炉里烧得劈啪作响。

sentences.english: The boys chopped wood, splitting the enormous logs in the woodshed into manageable pieces.
sentences.chinese: 男人在劈柴，他把柴棚里的原木劈成小块。

sentences.english: Every day, after other workers finished loading up logs, he began to work.
sentences.chinese: 每天在其他工人装载完原木后他就开始工作了。

sentences.english: The logs are shipped to a mill in San Leandro, California.
sentences.chinese: 原木被装船送到加利福尼亚的圣安德鲁斯打磨。

sentences.english: The solid tube of newsprint will burn much like a log in the fireplace.
sentences.chinese: 在壁炉中坚实的报纸管将燃烧得同原木一样。

sentences.english: All the trees have been sawn up into logs .
sentences.chinese: 所有的树已被锯成原木。

sentences.english: Bulwarks on upper deck where deck log cargoes to be loaded, shall be designed to suit accordingly.
sentences.chinese: 甲板上要装原木的舷墙应该根据需要设计。

sentences.english: The company's products are mainly large-scale wood carving eagles.
sentences.chinese: 本公司的产品主要大型原木鹰雕。

sentences.english: In this paper, the authors expound the principles of tree-length measuring design and management methods of logs checked and accepted.
sentences.chinese: 本文论述了原条量材设计原则及原木验收管理办法。
